= Technical Information =
The website whonix.org, takes your privacy seriously and collects as little as information as possible. IP logs are disabled, we are using apache mod-removeip <ref>https://we.riseup.net/debian/apache#mod_removeip</ref>. If it becomes necessary (such as spamming or abuse), we may need to re-enable IP logging. 

In any case, we recommend visiting this website using the Tor Browser in Whonix or using the Tor Browser Bundle. Although we rent this server from a reputable server provider, but can't audit their logging policy.

A written privacy policy is not worth much anyway, since its only privacy by policy. That is why anonymity preserving tools such as Whonix and Tor Browser have been created in the first place. They offer privacy by design.

